high_descs: Turn left and go forward to the white table, then turn right to face the black table.
Pick up the fork on the black table.
Turn right and move forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Wash the fork in the sink.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right to go toward the white table, then turn right to face the black table.
Put the fork on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork on the black table.

high_descs: Make a left and then walk to the far right corner of the room, where a small black table is on the left of a white table.
Pick up the fork from the small black table.
Make a right to walk to the sink.
Rinse the fork in the sink, removing it again.
Turn left to walk towards the small black table next to the white table.
Set the fork down on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Wash a fork and put it back on the black table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward across the room to the toaster, then turn right and walk to the small black side table.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the fork in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn left and walk back to the small side table.
Put the fork back on the table, in front of the closest salt container.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned fork on a small side table.
